        <item>
            <title>Version 1.3</title>
            <pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 22:45:45 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>1.3</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.3</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <description><![CDATA[<html><head><style>body{font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'SF Pro Text',sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#1c1c1e;background:#fff;margin:0;padding:14px 18px 10px;line-height:1.6}ul{margin:0;padding-left:18px}li{margin-bottom:6px}b{color:#6d28d9}</style></head><body><ul><li><b>Custom Folder destination</b> — pick any folder on your Mac (NAS, RAID, internal drive); date folders still auto-created inside</li><li><b>Light mode contrast overhaul</b> — deeper blue and purple across all UI elements, ring, pills, and queue rows</li><li><b>Smooth scrolling</b> — all panels use AppKit-backed momentum scrolling with elastic bounce</li><li><b>Speed graph instant start</b> — appears when a transfer begins instead of after 10–15 seconds</li><li><b>History panel</b> now resets at the broadcast-day cutoff instead of a fixed 24 hours</li><li><b>Destination tabs</b> have a sliding pill animation, hover states, and full-area click targets</li><li><b>Stale path detection</b> — orange warning on launch if the chosen custom folder is missing or unmounted</li></ul></body></html>]]></description>
            <enclosure
                url="https://github.com/Xtron6/-cardrunner-releases/releases/download/v1.3/CardRunner-1.3.dmg"
                sparkle:edSignature="zI3XTD9YltTGiiHdLWYnIwBTObw0s0AQMDmlHL06XVmW6BppKg5TJLqGEHMXxly1aW56a/eIgEX4VL9LHKXZBQ=="
                length="5526716"
