        </item>

        <item>
            <title>Version 1.4</title>
            <pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 17:25:29 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>4</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.4</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <description><![CDATA[<html><head><style>body{font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'SF Pro Text',sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#1c1c1e;background:#fff;margin:0;padding:14px 18px 10px;line-height:1.6}ul{margin:0;padding-left:18px}li{margin-bottom:6px}b{color:#6d28d9}</style></head><body><ul><li><b>Sparkle auto-update</b> — existing users will receive this and all future updates automatically</li><li><b>Custom date filter</b> — pick any date from a graphical calendar or type MM/DD/YYYY</li><li><b>Debug mode</b> — new toggle in Advanced reveals the Log panel and Dry Run toggle</li><li><b>Daily log rotation</b> — logs roll over each day and are kept for 7 days</li><li><b>Transfer speed fix</b> — eliminated a near-100% hang on large card ingests</li><li><b>Destination path preview</b> updates dynamically with your actual folder name and date format</li></ul></body></html>]]></description>
