        <item>
            <title>Version 1.4.2</title>
            <pubDate>Thu, 23 Apr 2026 13:22:31 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>6</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.4.2</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <description><![CDATA[<html><head><style>body{font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'SF Pro Text',sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#1c1c1e;background:#fff;margin:0;padding:14px 18px 10px;line-height:1.6}ul{margin:0;padding-left:18px}li{margin-bottom:6px}b{color:#6d28d9}</style></head><body><ul><li><b>XMP sidecar support</b> — color labels, ratings, and metadata from Photo Mechanic, Lightroom, and Capture One now transfer with your photos automatically</li><li><b>Up to 30× faster transfer start</b> on large photo cards — batch stat pre-fetch replaces thousands of individual shell calls</li><li><b>Speed graph fixed</b> — appears immediately when copying starts instead of staying blank</li><li><b>Completion sound fixed</b> — no more echo or stutter on large transfers</li><li><b>Phase timing in logs</b> — every run records how long scanning, building, and copying took for easier debugging</li></ul></body></html>]]></description>
